  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dbd\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0da9\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "All schools are off for a week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education has decided to give holidays to all schools in the island this week.",
        "According to an announcement issued by the Ministry of Education, the period from tomorrow (4th) to Friday (8th) will be designated as a holiday week for all schools in the island.",
        "This decision was taken in the discussion held today (3) through Zoom technology with officials of the Ministry of Education, Provincial Education Secretaries and Provincial Education Directors.",
        "After reviewing the progress of school principals, teachers and students in the last fortnight and also taking into account the notices of the Ministry of Power and Energy regarding fuel distribution, this week has been declared as a holiday week for all government schools and government approved private schools across the island. According to the announcement.",
        "It also states that the school time lost during this week will be covered in the upcoming school holidays."
      ],
